-- 4. Detangle AI
('detangle-ai', 'Detangle AI', 'Plain-language summaries of legal documents and contracts for non-lawyers',
'Detangle AI is a document simplification tool that translates complex legal documents into plain language, making contracts, terms of service, privacy policies, and legal agreements understandable to non-lawyers. Users upload or paste a legal document and receive a plain-language summary, a breakdown of key clauses, and highlighted sections that deserve particular attention before signing. This makes Detangle valuable both for individuals reviewing contracts and for legal teams explaining complex agreements to clients or business stakeholders without legal training. The free tier covers a limited number of documents per day. Paid plans remove usage limits and add features including contract comparison and priority processing. Detangle does not provide legal advice and positions itself as a document comprehension tool that helps users know the right questions to ask a lawyer, rather than replacing legal counsel entirely. For small business owners, freelancers, and non-legal professionals who regularly encounter contracts they struggle to parse, Detangle provides accessible document clarity without requiring a legal consultation for routine agreement review.',
'https://www.google.com/s2/favicons?domain=detangle.ai&sz=64',
'https://detangle.ai', 'https://detangle.ai',
