-- 8. DocuSign AI
('docusign-ai', 'DocuSign IAM', 'AI agreement intelligence on top of the world''s leading e-signature platform',
'DocuSign is the global standard for e-signatures, trusted by over one million customers across 180 countries. DocuSign IAM (Intelligent Agreement Management) extends the platform with AI-powered contract intelligence, adding obligation extraction, renewal tracking, and automated agreement analysis to the signing workflow that organisations already rely on. For companies that use DocuSign for e-signatures, the IAM features unlock contract data previously locked in signed PDFs, extracting payment terms, renewal clauses, and obligations into a structured, searchable format. DocuSign IAM includes pre-built AI models for specific document types including NDAs, employment agreements, and sales contracts. The platform integrates natively with Salesforce, Microsoft 365, SAP, and major HR platforms. Basic e-signature plans start at $15 per month. The AI features are available on Business Pro and higher plans. DocuSign''s breadth of integrations and global adoption make it the practical default for organisations adding AI to a signing workflow that already runs on DocuSign.',
