-- 9. Adobe Sign
('adobe-sign', 'Adobe Acrobat Sign', 'AI-enhanced e-signatures integrated with Adobe PDF editing and document creation tools',
'Adobe Acrobat Sign is Adobe''s enterprise e-signature and agreement management solution, integrated directly into the Acrobat PDF editing workflow that businesses rely on for document creation. The AI capabilities, powered by Adobe Sensei, include automatic form field detection, signature placement intelligence, and document summarisation through the Acrobat AI Assistant. For organisations that create documents in Acrobat and collect signatures in the same ecosystem, Adobe Sign provides the tightest integration between document creation and signature collection. The platform handles routing, tracking, and archiving of signed documents within the Adobe Document Cloud environment. Individual plans start at $16.99 per month. Team and enterprise tiers include advanced workflow automation, custom branding, and government compliance certifications. Adobe Sign is particularly strong for document-intensive industries where the entire creation-to-signature workflow lives within the Adobe ecosystem, including legal, financial services, and government organisations.',
